# Project Structure

This is a React TypeScript portfolio website built with Vite and styled with Tailwind CSS.

The main files and directories are:

- [index.html](mdc:index.html): The entry point HTML file
- [src/main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx): The main React entry point
- [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx): The root React component
- [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css): Global styles including Tailwind CSS
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js): Tailwind configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts
